            "heading": "White in, white out.",
            "heading_italic": "Every ride",
            "description": "<p>This overshoe is more than just protection for the serious cyclist. Our design leaves no room for compromise — no loose fits, no soaked feet, no dirty white after one ride. Built for road and off-road use, crafted for those who refuse to sacrifice style for function. When you want to ride comfortable, without pressure points, wet or muddy feet: this overshoe is what you need.</p>"
